  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ultimate Monkey Race</strong> is a chaotic <strong>3D party platform-racer</strong> where you and your friends <strong>build the level as you play</strong>. Drop blocks and traps in seconds, then run, jump, <strong>grab ledges and pull yourself up</strong> to recover or find cheeky shortcuts on the way to the goal. It’s fast to host, easy to learn, and best with friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create challenging levels by placing building pieces and traps:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/da63bac0fca0c1aa45e62248553c539c.poster.avif?t=1768434111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/da63bac0fca0c1aa45e62248553c539c.webm?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/da63bac0fca0c1aa45e62248553c539c.mp4?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make your way through the level and reach the finish line to score points:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/9ccf53d9a21250c48ea9510befcaaea0.poster.avif?t=1768434111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/9ccf53d9a21250c48ea9510befcaaea0.webm?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/9ccf53d9a21250c48ea9510befcaaea0.mp4?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The player with most points wins the round:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/a41edd81f6c007478e6955af46acc5c0.poster.avif?t=1768434111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/a41edd81f6c007478e6955af46acc5c0.webm?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/a41edd81f6c007478e6955af46acc5c0.mp4?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Parcour skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build challenging levels with your friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Huge selection of blocks to create a variety of levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Variety of levels with different challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Host or join a game via Steam with upto 6 players (hard limit is 32 players - but it is optimized for upto 6 players)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ingame communication: Voice chat / chat</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ultimate Monkey Race</strong> is a chaotic <strong>3D party platform-racer</strong> where you and your friends <strong>build the level as you play</strong>. Drop blocks and traps in seconds, then run, jump, <strong>grab ledges and pull yourself up</strong> to recover or find cheeky shortcuts on the way to the goal. It’s fast to host, easy to learn, and best with friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create challenging levels by placing building pieces and traps:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/da63bac0fca0c1aa45e62248553c539c.poster.avif?t=1768434111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/da63bac0fca0c1aa45e62248553c539c.webm?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/da63bac0fca0c1aa45e62248553c539c.mp4?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make your way through the level and reach the finish line to score points:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/9ccf53d9a21250c48ea9510befcaaea0.poster.avif?t=1768434111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/9ccf53d9a21250c48ea9510befcaaea0.webm?t=1768434111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847850/extras/9ccf53d9a21250c48ea9510befcaaea0.mp4?t=